59329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e488fbf115910583194eb21381bbc18037e6b28","tid":1775901,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b7f10bc15ab5c13ad0648d9083f6757bbf8968","tid":1775901,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece00678a10f859a48b51dfc2d5433e514d28999","tid":1775901,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">團體正尋找性暴力證人/受害者</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=581730c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"608143fbc2a0f1e8ff970c1ee56abfc933c5d3c9","tid":1775901,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1410e2d4bc8e84c07ca34b3fdaf74a50c72d8e94","tid":1775901,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d161767cc7484300b2fd2b872abe89675b8fa458","tid":1775901,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842564b78918faa9130e0ccace089c88dea694ee","tid":1775901,"uid":35763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"其實主要做咩搞到咁差"},{"pid":"1f07a1dce584ab12670f3e3ba861f5f909ffee54","tid":1775901,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"842564b78918faa9130e0ccace089c88dea694ee","tid":1775901,"uid":35763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"其實主要做咩搞到咁差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"真心希望大家唔好再亂屌人<br />\n連登都好多人比人亂屌分化撚、一毛<br />\n屌到心淡"},{"pid":"bde00f5d8335cfc72d7917d12432127a541b9f04","tid":1775901,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01f9d5e1466c6449bc9ff810d7c582c8d2558dbc","tid":1775901,"uid":144492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:16:10.000Z","msg":"台灣嗰邊風向一形成咗就好麻煩<br />\n而家唔到我地唔認衰<br />\n的確係嗰兩位學界手足寫到人地奉旨幫咁<br />\n大佬呀 你對住trump又唔見你屌佢食人血饅頭<br />\n叫人幫唔係用呢種態度囉<br />\n最好笑係你叫韓國瑜承諾 有意義咩？<br />\n佢出咗名鳩up㗎啦 諗清楚自己定位啦<br />\n而家應該做嘅係等english連任先再同佢deal<br />\n佢喺呢一刻根本唔會冒險剩係serve香港人<br />\n人地係選台灣總統唔係香港總統"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"係個兩條柒頭皮冇野搵野搞<br />\n權衡利弊台仔跟本唔會扔手足番黎<br />\n又唔使佢出錢養 扔左番黎以後點打燈塔牌<br />\n不過而家兩條柒頭民主中國膠咁樣搞法就好難講了<br />\n台仔一向小氣"},{"pid":"9533cf4329bbf0d7ec5491baa8c63d47fb67b09f","tid":1775901,"uid":342966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1005fe32b79d628f1f8f8bda9a4e0c8c9e385f0","tid":1775901,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"蔡英文靠反送中上位就緊架啦<br />\n呢樣唔到佢唔認<br />\n<br />\n但係都係佢啫<br />\n唔關其他台灣人事<br />\n希望大家唔好亂咁鳩叫人血饅頭<br />\n好似呢到有啲傻閪係咪都鳩叫分化、屈毛<img src=\"/a